object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
      AND bls.target_table_name = '$$target_table_name'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
            AND target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
            AND target_table_name = '$$target_table_name'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT 
    bronze_scea.acx_search_criteria_ea_row_id,
    bronze_scea.acx_search_criteria_ea_batch_id,
    bronze_scea.originating_source_name         AS originating_source_name,
    bronze_scea.originating_load_type           AS originating_load_type,
    bronze_scea.acx_search_criteria_ea_row_md5checksum,
    bronze_scea.acx_search_criteria_ea_row_effective_start_datetime,
    bronze_scea.acx_search_criteria_ea_row_effective_end_datetime,
    bronze_scea.acx_search_criteria_ea_row_status,
    bronze_scea.system_id                       AS source_system_system_id,
    bronze_scea.parent_id                       AS source_system_parent_id,
    bronze_scea.cmm_container                   AS predictive_analytics_search_criteria_type,
    bronze_scea.id                              AS predictive_analytics_search_criteria_row_source_system_key,
    bronze_scea.search_criteria_name            AS search_criteria_name,
    bronze_scea.search_criteria_value           AS search_criteria_value,
    bronze_scea.type                            AS source_system_type,
    bronze_scea.key_parent_bean_ref_id          AS key_parent_bean_reference_id,
    bronze_scea.row_id                          AS source_system_row_id,
    cb.batch_id                                 AS batch_id,
    silver_sc.predictive_analytics_search_criteria_id,
    silver_sc.predictive_analytics_search_criteria_row_md5checksum
FROM $$staging_schema.acx_search_criteria_ea bronze_scea
LEFT JOIN $$refined_schema.predictive_analytics_search_criteria silver_sc
    ON COALESCE(TRIM(bronze_scea.id), '') = COALESCE(CAST(silver_sc.predictive_analytics_search_criteria_row_source_system_key AS VARCHAR), '')
   AND CAST(TRIM(bronze_scea.system_id) AS INT) = CAST(silver_sc.source_system_system_id AS INT)
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(bronze_scea.cmm_container), '') = COALESCE(silver_sc.predictive_analytics_search_criteria_type, '')
   AND silver_sc.predictive_analytics_search_criteria_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
   AND silver_sc.predictive_analytics_search_criteria_row_status = 'Active'
CROSS JOIN current_batch cb
WHERE bronze_scea.acx_search_criteria_ea_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
ORDER BY 
    bronze_scea.system_id,
    bronze_scea.cmm_container,
    bronze_scea.id;
